Why do you make the interface members non-optional and instead make the whole interface later in `init`/`load` `Partial`? It's not very ergonomic for your users and it increases compile times. You should instead make all of the interface members optional:
```ts
export interface Settings {
    watermark_id?: string;
    watermark_prefix?: string;
    watermark_txt?: string;
    watermark_x?: number;
    ...
}
```

